Speaker 1: Hi, thank you so much for calling Viagra.

Speaker 2: That score blue, how can I help you today?

Speaker 1: Yes, I called and canceled

Speaker 1: And I'm gonna have to dispute with PayPal

Speaker 1: You guys have to stop sending me stuff.

Speaker 2: Okay, sir, let me just pull up your account here

Speaker 1: and see what happened.

Speaker 2: Can I get your full name and date of birth?

Speaker 1: Terry Bangy, 072061.

Speaker 2: Okay, Terry, so I'm looking at your script right now.

Speaker 1: The original script was written on December 20th.

Speaker 2: Okay, and then you had called

Speaker 1: and stopped the prescription altogether on the 21st.

Speaker 2: Okay. Yes, I did.

Speaker 1: Okay, so what happened was a refill was...

Speaker 2: I'm not sure if the person mentioned this to you,

Speaker 1: but you had a refill that went through before that canceled.

Speaker 2: So it's canceled,

Speaker 1: but the prescription already went out

Speaker 2: before you stopped it.

Speaker 1: So if you don't want it, you just need to return it,

Speaker 2: but it's canceled.

Speaker 1: Okay, but I have to pay for the return on this?

Speaker 2: No, not at all.

Speaker 1: You just put return to sender on that original packaging.

Speaker 2: Okay, I'm gonna do that right now

Speaker 1: and I'm gonna go drop it off.

Speaker 2: Yeah, you put return to sender on there,

Speaker 1: put it back in your mailbox or drop it off at USPS.

Speaker 2: It'll be issued a refund, but this is closed out.

Speaker 1: Yeah, Terry, you don't have anything to worry about.

Speaker 2: It's canceled.

Speaker 1: All right, I just want to make sure I get...

Speaker 2: And I'm gonna get my money back.

Speaker 1: Yes, sir, you put return to sender.

Speaker 2: As soon as it's filed with us, you'd be issued a refund.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: And that's for both prescriptions?

Speaker 1: They're sending me two different ones.

Speaker 2: I got...

Speaker 1: Do you have multiple accounts?

Speaker 2: Because I only see two prescriptions here.

Speaker 1: I see the original one placed on December 20th

Speaker 2: and I see the refill.

Speaker 1: Okay, and what's that one for, that you have on there?

Speaker 2: This is for the 100 milligram Viagra, AGV.

Speaker 1: And it comes in a...

Speaker 2: Secret handbook comes in it?

Speaker 1: A secret handbook?

Speaker 2: And it's coming from...

Speaker 1: What's it coming from?

Speaker 2: NABIGYM Pharmaceuticals?

Speaker 1: Sir, that's not us.

Speaker 2: Who in the heck is this?

Speaker 1: Why are they sending me this stuff?

Speaker 2: I did not order this.

Speaker 1: Yeah, that's not us.

Speaker 2: Our company's based out of Kentucky.

Speaker 1: And it would be Scor-Blue and Go-Go Meds.

Speaker 2: Yeah, these are Friday Plans.

Speaker 1: Yeah, Friday Plans is not us.

Speaker 2: That's a completely different company.

Speaker 1: Okay, now the other one I sent back.

Speaker 2: You guys haven't got it back yet?

Speaker 1: Let me see here.

Speaker 2: No, sir, so the one that was delivered in Bakersfield

Speaker 1: has not been returned yet.

Speaker 2: All right, and what was the price on that?

Speaker 1: $63.95.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's what I got on there.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: But what you're holding in your hand,

Speaker 1: Friday Plans is not us.

Speaker 2: I don't know, who sent me this?

Speaker 1: Why would they send me this stuff?

Speaker 2: Friday Plans is another telehealth service

Speaker 1: that also does erectile dysfunction pills.

Speaker 2: But Friday Plans is not FDA approved

Speaker 1: and it is not a Scor-Blue.

Speaker 2: They are not the same thing.

Speaker 1: I've never ordered this, so all right.

Speaker 2: I'm going to figure this out.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Uh-huh, thank you.
